              <td class="news_e">華語文能力測驗（電腦適性化測驗）正式考試將在1月14日舉行，報名時間從12月12日起至12月28日止，歡迎母語非華語之人士報考。名額有限，請儘早報名！&nbsp;<br />
 [<a href="https://reg.sc-top.org.tw/" target="_blank">我要報名</a>] [<a href="http://www.sc-top.org.tw/download/CAT20170114.pdf" target="_blank">測驗海報</a>] [<a href="http://www.sc-top.org.tw/download/CAT_announcement.pdf" target="_blank">公告事項</a>] [<a href="http://www.sc-top.org.tw/download/CAT_QA.pdf" target="_blank">Q&A</a>]<br /><span class="style38">※<strong>請在報名完成後三天內繳費</strong></span>，以免報名失效<strong>。</strong><br />
Please  be notified that the formal TOCFL adopt computerized adaptive test (CAT) will  be administered on January 14. The registration period is from  December  12 to  December 28. Welcome the candidates who are non-native speakers of  Chinese to take the test. The test seats are limited, seize the chance!<br />&nbsp;<a href="https://reg.sc-top.org.tw/" target="_blank">[Register for Test</a>] [<a href="http://www.sc-top.org.tw/download/CAT20170114.pdf" target="_blank">Poster</a>] [<a href="http://www.sc-top.org.tw/download/CAT_announcement.pdf" target="_blank">Announcement</a>] [<a href="http://www.sc-top.org.tw/download/CAT_QA.pdf" target="_blank">Q&A</a>]<br />※To secure your slot, you must<span class="style38"><strong><strong>&nbsp;make your payment in 3 days once you register.</strong></strong></span></td>
