                In 2015, TOCFL's Listening and Reading Tests on Band A will each adopt an additional section of test items. There will be a Dialogue section in the Listening Test and a Reading Comprehension section in the Reading Test.[<a href="download/入門基礎級測驗題型變更說明.pdf" target="_blank">Updates to Test Section Addition in the TOCFL Band A</a>]</td>
